          "_name": "features022",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features22\" group=\"Features\" plugins=\"Masonry\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\" checked>\n    <header>Card</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icons\" name=\"showIcon\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#00e363\" selected condition=\"showIcon\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon BG\" name=\"iconbg\" value=\"#181d23\" selected condition=\"showIcon\">\n    <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n      <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n      <option value=\"6\" selected>2</option>\n      <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n      <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n    </select>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#181d23\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row mb-5 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Como eu faço seu negócio atrair</b><br><b> clientes no digital.</b></h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">Um processo completo, do planejamento até o cliente chegar no seu WhatsApp.</h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row mbr-masonry\" data-masonry=\"{&quot;percentPosition&quot;: true }\">\n      \n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb active\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-idea mobi-mbri\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b><i>Diagnóstico</i></b><br></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><i>Encontrando o que está travando seu crescimento</i><br><br>👉 Antes de qualquer ação, eu entendo seu negócio e descubro onde está o problema.<br><br>👉 Você para de postar sem rumo e começa a ter direção.<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-magic-stick\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Design</b></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><i>Fazendo sua marca parecer&nbsp;</i><i>profissional<br></i><br>👉 Organizo seu visual e crio conteúdos que passam confiança e chamam atenção.<br><br>👉 Seu perfil deixa de parecer amador e começa a gerar interesse.<br><br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-video mobi-mbri\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Dinâmica</b></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><i>Conteúdo que prende e faz agir</i><br><br>👉 Transformo ideias simples em vídeos e conteúdos que realmente conectam.<br><br>👉 As pessoas param, assistem e começam a se interessar.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-rocket\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Distribuição</b></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\"><i>Colocando você na frente das pessoas certas</i><br><br>👉 Levo seu conteúdo até quem realmente pode virar cliente.<br><br>👉 Mais mensagens no WhatsApp e mais oportunidades de venda.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      \n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
