          "_name": "news06",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"news06\" group=\"News\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' &amp;&amp; bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline=\"\" title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline=\"\" title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n    <header>Image</header>\n    <input type=\"range\" inline=\"\" title=\"Height\" name=\"imageHeight\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline=\"\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Main Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Main Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked=\"\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Price\" name=\"showPrice\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked=\"\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n    <header>Color</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"rowColor\" value=\"#181d23\" selected=\"\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax=\"\">\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/banner2-2000x1125.png\" parallax=\"\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#20272f\" selected=\"\">\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay &amp;&amp; bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline=\"\" title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay &amp;&amp; bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay &amp;&amp; bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mbr-section-maintitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-maintitle\">\n          <b>Our events</b>\n        </h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4 mbr-section-mainsubtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-mainsubtitle\">\n          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent vitae erat. Integer aliquam, lorem\n          vitae dapibus sollicitudin, nibh nisl egestas enim, ut dapibus odio augue tempus venenatis mi\n          semper.\n        </h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center align-items-center item features-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 \">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n              <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/a-hyper-realistic-professional-202603220207-1076x601.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg col-md-12\">\n              <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Até quando você vai deixar seu negócio parado?</b></h5>\n                <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                  July 12-13, 2025\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Se você sente que poderia estar vendendo mais, mas seu Instagram não ajuda… Se suas redes não geram mensagens… Se sua marca não passa confiança… <br><br>O problema não é seu negócio, o&nbsp;problema é a forma como ele está sendo apresentado. E isso tem solução. Você não precisa aprender marketing, nem perder tempo tentando acertar sozinho.<br><br><b><i>Você só precisa da estratégia certa, aplicada do jeito certo.</i></b><br><br>Enquanto você está decidindo, tem concorrente seu aparecendo mais, sendo lembrado e fechando cliente.<br><br><i><b>A</b></i><b><i> diferença entre vocês não é o produto. É a presença.<br></i></b></p>\n                <div mbr-buttons=\"\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                  <a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-white\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                    Learn more\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n  </div>\n</section>",
